description: Times, periods, or points related to the start, beginning, first stage, onset, or early phases of events, things, or processes, or to initial steps or stages within a multi-stage process
Times or dates, often in relation to a specific event or season
Importance, influence, significance, effect, impact, especially when related to first times, most, best, biggest, or very large quantities or magnitudes
Superlative adjectives related to size, quantity, or quality in contexts of comparisons or rankings
Ordinal numbers, especially in contexts of rankings, lists, and time sequences
